OL,3,CElection politicking or protecting
OL,4,Cservices? Rivals row over Borders
OL,5,Cbudget
OL,7,FWould you have guessed there's an
OL,8,Felection in less than three months?
OL,10,FThere has been a pretty consensual
OL,11,Fapproach to setting the Scottish
OL,12,FBorders council budget in recent years
OL,13,Fafter leader Euan Jardine encouraged
OL,14,Fcross-party working.
OL,16,FThat is falling apart this year after
OL,17,Fthe Conservative politician proposed
OL,18,Fan 8.5% increase in council tax.
