OL,7,FCosla, the umbrella group that
OL,8,Frepresents councils, has been highly
OL,9,Fcritical of the local government
OL,10,Fsettlement contained in the Holyrood
OL,11,Fbudget.
OL,13,FOne senior figure in an SNP-controlled
OL,14,Fcouncil said privately recently they
OL,15,Fwere prepared to "see the whites of
OL,16,Fministers' eyes" over the cash
OL,17,Fsettlement.
