OL,3,CElection politicking or protecting
OL,4,Cservices? Rivals row over Borders
OL,5,Cbudget
OL,7,FThat's just over #600,000 for each
OL,8,Fcouncil if it is split evenly and it
OL,9,Fis far from clear that it will satisfy
OL,10,Fangry local authorities who want #750
OL,11,Fmillion more to be shared across
OL,12,FScotland.
OL,14,FBut the funding was enough in a
OL,15,Fpackage to buy off the Liberal
OL,16,FDemocrats, who have announced they
OL,17,Fwill back the Holyrood budget.
